r1.zebra:
log record-priority
log timestamp precision 6
!
hostname r1
service advanced-vty
!
    interface r1-noprot
     description noprot
     no link-detect
    !
    interface r1-rip
     description rip
     no link-detect
    !
    interface r1-ripng
     description ripng
     no link-detect
    !
    interface r1-ospfv2
     description ospfv2
     no link-detect
    !
    interface r1-ospfv3
     description ospfv3
     no link-detect
    !
    interface r1-isisv4
     description isisv4
     no link-detect
    !
    interface r1-isisv6
     description isisv6
     no link-detect
    !
    !
    ip forwarding
    ipv6 forwarding
    !
!
line vty
!
r1.ripd:
log record-priority
log timestamp precision 6
!
hostname r1
service advanced-vty
!
    debug rip events
    debug rip zebra
    !
    router rip
     version 2
     network 10.1.0.0/16
!
line vty
!
r1.ripngd:
log record-priority
log timestamp precision 6
!
hostname r1
service advanced-vty
!
    debug ripng events
    debug ripng zebra
    !
    router ripng
     network fc00:0:0:1::/64
!
line vty
!
